  "texts": [
    "Although feedback is an essential and integral component of essay writing in educational settings, its study within the context of deep learning-based AES models is relatively limited.",
    "Identifying the essay components that contribute to the overall score can be a valuable task as it enables writers to identify the weak areas within their essays and improve upon them.",
    "Therefore, investigating neural feedback-based methods would be a promising research direction to enhance the effectiveness of AES models and provide more insightful feedback to writers.",
    "This survey paper discusses various deep learning-based AES models that excel at identifying complex patterns within essays.",
    "However, understanding the internal workings of these models and their relationship with predicted scores can be challenging."
  ],
